ggpairs(seattle_tidy)

seattle_tidy_numeric <- seattle_tidy %>%
  select_if(is.numeric)

seattle_tidy_nonnumeric <- seattle_tidy %>%
  select_if(function(x) !is.numeric(x))

seattle_tidy_nonnumeric$price <- seattle_tidy$price
